title: Rand Paul said he hopes trucker protests 'clog up cities,' including during Super Bowl and in DC - CNN
content:

description: While protests by truckers and others against Covid mandates continue to occupy Canada's capital, block US-Canada border crossings and add to supply chain headaches, Republican Sen. Rand Paul of Kentucky said he hopes trucker protests come to the United States as soon as this weekend to "clog up" major US cities.
